			Profile
			
			JianyiYANGwasbornin1969.HereceivedtheB.S.degree,theM.S.degreeandthePh.D.degreefromZhejiangUniversity,China,in1991,1994,and1996,respectively.Then,hejoinedthefacultyofZhejiangUniversity.HebecameanassociateprofessorofDepartmentofInformationScienceandElectronicsEngineering,ZhejiangUniversity,in1998.FromAug.2000toNov.2002,hewasworkingasapostdocintheMicroelectronicResearchCenter,theUniversityofTexasatAustin.HebecameafullprofessorofZhejiangUniversityin2003.Hisresearchareascoverintegratedopticsforopticalcommunication,opticalinterconnection,andopticalsignalprocessing.Hehasover100publicationsinprestigiousinternationaljournalsandconferences.Heholdsabout20Chinesepatents.HeisamemberofIEEEandOSA.
			
				
